 />\n<br />\n之前exchange整個比瑞士朋友<br />\n我9up話係港式pizza 佢讚不絕口<br />\n到而家都成日整俾朋友食"},{"pid":"6f624c301614965e0b1e96f72d118f4e4bae901d","tid":1044804,"uid":55917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T08:20:39.000Z","msg":"唔煮 直接食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ed69bc0361d412d9a21de559bd6b7c9bbf6746d","tid":1044804,"uid":55177,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T17:37:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}